summary: Captain marvel is the first superhero movie where a hero with powers on the level of superman actually uses their powers to fuck...
body:
Captain marvel is the first superhero movie where a hero with powers on the level of superman actually uses their powers to fuck shit up sigle-handily in space.


Like out of all the superman movies or movies with other space heroes (guardians, green lantern, fantastic four, hell even star trek) I’ve never seen a hero actually exude the powers that they supposedly have on such a scale. Usually the fights are confined to a downtown measly human city, or maybe ship on ship battles…but watching that last fight scene with captain marvel against Ronan the Accurser’s ships and warheads…my mind was just BLOWN.

summary:
I still can't believe that people are mad that Captain Marvel has lipstick on in Endgame trailer. Lol! 
That's most definitely...
body:
I still can’t believe that people are mad that Captain Marvel has lipstick on in Endgame trailer. Lol!

That’s most definitely Natasha’s lipstick and Carol just wants to know what it’s like wearing some… since you know she didn’t get a chance to wear some in 25 years. 😳😳😳 Brie Larson was also wearing makeup in Captain Marvel if you’ll didn’t notice.
